image_analysis.description: A nighttime photograph of a building facade with two cars parked in front. The building is a multi-story stone structure with ornate architectural details, including arched windows with decorative keystones and a large, arched wooden double door. A single lantern is lit above the main entrance. Two trees flank the entrance. A dark blue sedan is parked on the left, and a silver SUV (Toyota Highlander Limited) is parked on the right. An orange construction barrier is visible on the far right.
